snippet.title: ChainStaff - Official Reveal Teaser Trailer | Guerrilla Collective 2024
snippet.description: Watch the ChainStaff reveal teaser trailer for a peek at this upcoming action-platformer game that is coming to PC. A full reveal of ChainStaff will be available on June 7, 2024. ChainStaff is a brutal action platformer with a transforming grappling hook and blazing weapon upgrades. To save Earth from the Star Spores, you’ll have to swing, shoot, and spear your way through hordes of mutating monsters and bone-shaking boss fights.
